  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p dir=\"ltr\">This hooded lantern appears to shimmer when lit, almost as if it is flickering between this world and another. It functions as a @Compendium[dnd5e.items.7FLs8qIGdOFnz9oL]{Lantern of Revealing}, but has the following powers as well:</p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6de6c08f-7fff-0209-49a0-643069951101\"></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Any creature on the ethereal plane that enters or starts its turn in the radius of the lantern’s light must succeed a DC 13 Charisma save or be instantly forced onto the material plane.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Any creature within the radius of the lantern’s light must succeed a DC 13 Charisma save to leave the light’s radius or to leave the material plane. </p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
